<DOCHDR>
http://server.soros.org:80/lindesmith/interest/costsof.html 204.168.83.130 19970112140338 text/html 10558
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 12 Jan 1997 13:57:33 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
