<center><h3>Drugs and Drug Policy: A Bibliography of Books and Reports</h3></center> 
<hr> 
<p><a name="top"></a> 
<center><h2>I. DRUG POLICY</h2></center> 
<dl> 
<dt> 
<dd>A. <a href="tlcbib1.html#ia">Drug Policy Analysis</a><br> 
B. <a href="tlcbib1.html#ib">Readers/Collections on Drugs & Drug Policy</a><br> 
