G. <a href="tlcbib1.html#ig">Drug Regulation: History & Policy</a><br> 
H. <a href="tlcbib1.html#ih">Alcohol Prohibition: Repeal and Alternatives</a><br> 
I. <a href="tlcbib1.html#ii">U.S. Congress</a><br> 
J. <a href="tlcbib1.html#ij">Drug Prohibition and its Alternatives</a><br> 
