<title>
Memory and Mourning: American Expressions of Grief
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="FFFFFF">
<table border=0 cellpadding=6>
<tr>
<td valign=top><img align=middle src=memory.jpg alt=#></td>
<td><font color="3640B7"><font size=+5>
Memory and Mourning:</font></font><br><font color="b87333"><font size=+4> 
<i>American Expressions of Grief</i> </font></font></td>
</table>

<img align=middle src=bar3.gif alt=#><p>

<font color="3640B7">Memory and Mourning is a traveling, interpretivie 
exhibition on loan from
the Strong Museum in Rochester, N.Y. blending historical artifacts and
documents, images, interactive stations, and historical analysis to
examine the cultural history of grief and its changing outward expression
in America from 1850 to 1993.</font><p>
<img align=middle src=bar3.gif alt=#><p>
