<title>The Lindesmith Center--GAO</title> 
</head> 
<body bgcolor="FFFFFF" link="006699" vlink="339999" text="000000">
<center><h4>THE LINDESMITH CENTER</h4></center> 
<center><img align=middle src=line.gif width=600 alt=#></center><br> 
 
 
<H2><center>General Accounting Office (GAO)</center></h2> 
 
<p><IMG src="point.gif"> 
You can check the 1994 and 1995 <a href="http://thorplus.lib.purdue.edu/gpo">GAO 
Blue Book reports</a> on their web site. When you get into this site, put an X in the 
GAO Blue Books box and any other relevant boxes, and enter a search term (drugs, 
money laundering, etc.). We will bring you additional relevant GAO reports in the 
future.</p> 
<p>
<hr> 
<p> 
<center>
