<head><title>RIP Clearinghouse: Internet Infrastructure and Support 
Resources</title> </head>

<!*****This page is part of the clearinghouse pages accessed from> 
<!*****clearinghouse.html.  The pages are:>
<!*****  infr_supp.html (infrastructure and support)
<!*****  act_serv.html,(activities and servicies)
<!*****  IRR.html (Internet-related resources)

